{"tid":1551734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各位阿sir，如果我係你 我會錄音同收集證據 為求自保以防被班大sir出賣","createTime":"2019-09-08T06:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T10:49:49.000Z","uid":222970,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f6989418d5fc169b8a4f89a8e3ef78353c9a93cb","tid":1551734,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"比我係警察，係依一刻我仲唔收集哂所有證據，仲要大大力支持成立獨立調查委員會。個乜鬼委員會咪又係只會查大粒唔查細嘅，個會查到幾千人咩？睇鉛水嗰次就知，42樓膠層咪又係只會射比啲細嘅食。所以一定要 keep 好哂啲對話同命令，拉啲膠層落馬。空左啲位出來邊個上位唔洗我教下話？<br />\n<br />\n即使成個運動完左<br />\n你以為政府唔會清算你班前線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有功就大sir拎<br />\n鑊就你地前線咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f89f9f34c649b8be8d03f00e169e94c854f40e","tid":1551734,"uid":147493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee36d5ffa0b4ad51111e3e16efeecba85221f7ad","tid":1551734,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"班大sir好古惑架 隨時set緊局比你踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac3bd014d1678285f51d9f62d292fec525e337e","tid":1551734,"uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">軍裝跑到死<br />\n<br />\n大sir嘆冷氣</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8b235e2eef60878528956b50d9e6e0ad1c447e0","tid":1551734,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"9e4f45f94f6b7610b118d450a189807bc15f8ea4","tid":1551734,"uid":135114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"佢哋自願幫大sir頂罪<br />\n大sir好，國家好"},{"pid":"8b12cbf3a324082a99a6ac02d3e9d87ff14e2b45","tid":1551734,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"大陸班公安武警亂咁黎<br />\n之後隻鑊留返畀香港警察揹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02ad6be1f6079787d6d59d80849a7ad654f1300","tid":1551734,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"唔係呀sir<br />\n<br />\n警察不是爵士<br />\n佢地係警員，警官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20492c8c1428b61854ab8c5bb2e1dd052ada769a","tid":1551734,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大把人出賣佢地佢地唔信咋嘛"},{"pid":"1b0ed4c9ba028904d00f93a9b3bfd13548377898","tid":1551734,"uid":39575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"sir 你老母"},{"pid":"1f34a5e7021421acd832389be606c1b04264c121","tid":1551734,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"各位阿sir 我真係唔係吹水<br />\n<br />\n你地以為自己幫個政府維穩係公義？<br />\n以為個政府日後會優待你？<br />\n<br />\n唔好傻啦 舉個例子 你睇返中共歷史<br />\n<br />\n當年林彪幫毛主席建國打江山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後？最係咪又係比中共殺全家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以如果831太子事件你知情的話 我建議你爆料 然後再去美領事尋求庇護<br />\n<br />\n否則你既下場將會被清算，係中共清算你啊 唔係香港人啊"},{"pid":"8c471c865cf95d1c6a4d625cd679c7b878c7ea03","tid":1551734,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"做大緊係推細去死<br />\n無論你打邊份工都係咁架啦<br />\n所有CAM都係影住班細既 做過火行為<br />\n到有事既時候<br />\n班大就話 叫左佢地唔好咁做 佢地都係照做<br />\n麻煩佢地自己承擔返責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88536a83d5f76c4554ca0e1730037473a8f7a1ef","tid":1551734,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b12cbf3a324082a99a6ac02d3e9d87ff14e2b45","tid":1551734,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"大陸班公安武警亂咁黎<br />\n之後隻鑊留返畀香港警察揹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:01:39.000Z","msg":"呢個真 班解放軍錯手殺人唔會有責任<br />\n<br />\n到時大sir推班前線咩左隻鑊佢<br />\n<br />\n警察？只係一隻政治棋子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7685e3aa80c7f249dccf961fd0a4143a71cba95","tid":1551734,"uid":270872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:02:23.000Z","msg":"大陸班公安武警亂黎<br />\n鑊又係前線香港警察頂<br />\n大sir功就自己領 <br />\n有事又係搵前線警察頂"},{"pid":"ebd678284c03dba664a6d0d8ad8e700d1fb63fe6","tid":1551734,"uid":304269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"其實佢地幫人食緊死猫⋯ <br />\n到時香港人真係會幫佢地咩？"},{"pid":"ea6c36408d87cc806ab96a70e9392fe48df03065","tid":1551734,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:04:04.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n冇理由自己食啲大sir嘅獲<br />\n唔死都整番佢地一身蟻"},{"pid":"acfe4f93a6fcbb3188b330df1b6d4d0e2633487f","tid":1551734,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382f53ce8744fd24b39855827e23a7770edc3d19","tid":1551734,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nb5pt5s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnb5pt5s.png&h=cab92c91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03d0963d255b613e7af41848fe7ed76b02d99527","tid":1551734,"uid":270872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"其實前線警察真係condom黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nor 好聽d係用完即棄既兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" c